## Done Means

- Run the relevant local verification for the area you changed.
- For backend changes, finish with `scripts/jig test`.
[% if sqlx_enabled %]
- For SQLx or migration changes, run `scripts/jig sqlx-check`.
[% if schema_dump_enabled %]
- For schema-doc-enabled repos, run `scripts/jig schema-check`.
[% endif %]
[% endif %]
- Review the generated diff for stale docs, policy drift, or missing dependent updates.

## Crate Guide Requirements

Every backend crate under the configured crate roots should have an `AGENTS.md` with these sections:

- `## Purpose`
- `## Key entrypoints`
- `## Edit here for X`
- `## Invariants`
- `## Common commands`
